name: T E A R D O W N
description:
[SIMULATANEON SERIES #002]

T E A R D O W N

The Tool will outgrow its Master, and Masters will become the lesser menace. The Obelisk will be toppled by the very ones who built it. It will be too late.

SIMULATANEON is a 2017 hypersigil and a conceptual prison break map for the upcoming matrix system update. The sigils that were borrowed for this series reveal only part of a bigger tapestry.
